Class DmaEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • platform.model.PlatformComponentProp
      • platform.model.DmaEngine

  • public class DmaEngine
extends PlatformComponentProp
    Represents a DMA Engine in the platform. A DMA Engine is attached to the cluster. We can add it to processor as well, but its not yet supported/required.
